## CORE CAPABILITIES

✦ **Forced Checkmate Detection** – Identifies positions where checkmate is unavoidable regardless of opponent defense

✦ **Moves-To-Mate Counter** – Displays exact number of moves until checkmate (M1, M2, M3... M20+)

✦ **Defensive Refutation** – Shows why opponent's defensive attempts fail against optimal play

✦ **Minimal Depth Setting** – Fast analysis for clear winning positions without over-calculation

✦ **FEN/PGN Import** – Load positions directly from games, puzzles, or online discussions

✦ **Visual Move Arrows** – Clear on-screen indication of winning continuations

✦ **Alternative Winning Lines** – Multiple checkmate paths when available

✦ **Stalemate Prevention** – Alerts when aggressive play might lead to draw instead of win

✦ **Endgame Tablebase Integration** – Perfect play for positions with 7 pieces or fewer

✦ **Save Analysis** – Export winning sequences for study or sharing

---

## TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS

▸ Engine: Optimized Stockfish 16 with mate-finding priority
▸ Depth: Adjustable from 10-40 ply
▸ Tablebases: Syzygy 7-piece (included)
▸ Formats: FEN, PGN, EPD
▸ Languages: English, Spanish, German, French
▸ Size: 45MB installed
▸ OS: Windows 7/8/10/11 (64-bit)

---

## POPULAR USE CASES

• **Puzzle Solving** – Verify your checkmate calculations against engine
• **Endgame Practice** – Learn exact winning methods in simplified positions
• **Game Review** – Check if you missed a faster checkmate
• **Teaching** – Show students why certain moves force victory
• **Opening Traps** – Identify early checkmate possibilities in sharp lines

